<ignored xmlns:e="http://exam.extension.io" xmlns:cc="http://www.concordion.org/2007/concordion">
    <h3>Core commands</h3>
    <hr/>
    <p>
        Core commands may be used to extend default Concordion possibilities of setting up, verifying and decorating of examples.
    </p>

    <h4>Usage</h4>
    <p>1. Add any exam dependency <pre class="doc-code"><code>testImplementation "io.github.adven27:exam-*:{{version}}"</code></pre></p>

    <h4>Commands</h4>
    <p>
        The following are core-commands available
    </p>

    <h5>Specification by example</h5>

    <dl>
        <dt><code><a cc:run="concordion" href="core/CoreExample.xhtml">example</a></code></dt>
        <dd>
            <p>Decorated version of <a href="https://concordion.org/instrumenting/java/html/#example-command">Concordion example command</a>:</p>
            <pre class="doc-code language-xml"><code> <![CDATA[
                <e:example name="Happy path">
                ...
                </e:example>
            ]]>
            </code></pre>
        </dd>
        <dt><code><a cc:run="concordion" href="core/CoreBeforeExample.xhtml">before-each</a></code></dt>
        <dd>
            <p>Custom version of <a href="https://concordion.org/instrumenting/java/html/#before-examples">Concordion before example command</a>:</p>
            <pre class="doc-code language-xml"><code> <![CDATA[
                <e:before-each>
                ...
                </e:before-each>
            ]]>
            </code></pre>
        </dd>
    </dl>

    <h5>Context variables setting</h5>

    <dl>
        <dt><code><a cc:run="concordion" href="core/CoreSet.xhtml">set</a></code></dt>
        <dd>
            <p>Handlebars-aware version of <a href="https://concordion.org/instrumenting/java/html/#set-command">Concordion set command</a>:</p>
            <pre class="doc-code language-xml"><code> <![CDATA[
                <pre e:set="dateVar">{{now}}</pre>
            ]]>
            </code></pre>
        </dd>
    </dl>

    <h5>Verifying</h5>

    <dl>
        <dt><code><a cc:run="concordion" href="core/CoreVerify.xhtml">equals</a></code></dt>
        <dd>
            <p>Handlebars-aware version of <a href="https://concordion.org/instrumenting/java/html/#assert-equals-command">Concordion assert command</a>:</p>
            <pre class="doc-code language-xml"><code><![CDATA[
                <span e:equals="actual">{{now}}</pre>
            ]]>
            </code></pre>
        </dd>
        <dt><code><a cc:run="concordion" href="core/CoreVerify.xhtml">equalsFile</a></code></dt>
        <dd>
            <p>Handlebars-aware version of <a href="https://concordion.org/instrumenting/java/html/#assert-equals-command">Concordion assert command</a>:</p>
            <pre class="doc-code language-xml"><code><![CDATA[
                <span e:equalsFile="actual">/data/expected.txt</pre>
            ]]>
            </code></pre>
        </dd>
        <dt><code><a cc:run="concordion" href="core/CoreVerify.xhtml">jsonEquals</a></code></dt>
        <dd>
            <p>Json-aware version of <a href="https://concordion.org/instrumenting/java/html/#assert-equals-command">Concordion assert command</a>:</p>
            <pre class="doc-code language-xml"><code><![CDATA[
                <span e:jsonEquals="actual">{"a" : 1}</pre>
            ]]>
            </code></pre>
        </dd>
        <dt><code><a cc:run="concordion" href="core/CoreVerify.xhtml">jsonEqualsFile</a></code></dt>
        <dd>
            <p>Json-aware version of <a href="https://concordion.org/instrumenting/java/html/#assert-equals-command">Concordion assert command</a>:</p>
            <pre class="doc-code language-xml"><code><![CDATA[
                <span e:jsonEqualsFile="actual">/data/expected.json</pre>
            ]]>
            </code></pre>
        </dd>
        <dt><code><a cc:run="concordion" href="core/CoreVerify.xhtml">xmlEquals</a></code></dt>
        <dd>
            <p>Xml-aware version of <a href="https://concordion.org/instrumenting/java/html/#assert-equals-command">Concordion assert command</a>:</p>
            <pre class="doc-code language-xml"><code><![CDATA[
                <span e:xmlEquals="actual">
                <! [CDATA[
                    <message>
                        <val>{{placeholder}}</val>
                    </message>
                ] ]>
                </pre>
            ]]>
            </code></pre>
        </dd>
        <dt><code><a cc:run="concordion" href="core/CoreVerify.xhtml">xmlEqualsFile</a></code></dt>
        <dd>
            <p>Xml-aware version of <a href="https://concordion.org/instrumenting/java/html/#assert-equals-command">Concordion assert command</a>:</p>
            <pre class="doc-code language-xml"><code><![CDATA[
                <span e:xmlEqualsFile="actual">/data/expected.xml</pre>
            ]]>
            </code></pre>
        </dd>
    </dl>

    <h5>Decorating</h5>

    <dl>
        <dt>
            <code><a cc:run="concordion" href="core/CoreDecor.xhtml">given</a></code>,
            <code><a cc:run="concordion" href="core/CoreDecor.xhtml">when</a></code>,
            <code><a cc:run="concordion" href="core/CoreDecor.xhtml">then</a></code>
        </dt>
        <dd>
            <p>Support of <a href="https://martinfowler.com/bliki/GivenWhenThen.html">the BDD-style</a> example description:</p>
            <pre class="doc-code language-xml"><code> <![CDATA[
                <e:given>
                ...
                </e:given>
                <e:when>
                ...
                </e:when>
                <e:then>
                ...
                </e:then>
            ]]>
            </code></pre>
        </dd>
    </dl>

</ignored>